016package de.cuioss.test.valueobjects.generator.dynamic.impl;
017
018import de.cuioss.test.generator.TypedGenerator;
019import de.cuioss.test.valueobjects.property.util.CollectionType;
020import lombok.NonNull;
021import lombok.RequiredArgsConstructor;
022
023/**
024 * Generator for Iterable / Collection interfaces
025 *
026 * @author Oliver Wolff
027 * @param <T> identifying the type to be generated
028 */
029@RequiredArgsConstructor
030public class CollectionTypeGenerator<T> implements TypedGenerator<T> {
031
032    @NonNull
033    private final Class<T> type;
034
035    @NonNull
036    private final CollectionType collectionType;
037
038    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")
039    @Override
040    public T next() {
041        return (T) collectionType.emptyCollection();
042    }
043
044    @Override
045    public Class<T> getType() {
046        return type;
047    }
048}
